Features
========

* bottom foreground for game over
* clear screen GFX
* puyo with different shapes
* puyo connection images
* print chain count during combos
* rotation animation
* multiplayer
* replays
* limit player name size in high scores (and allocate the string only once)
* Ready Set Go at the beginning of the game

Other
=====

* deterministic Rand module
* Gfx.set with arrays (using a bound on the length of effects)
